## Tech stack

Python 3.14, discord.py, Anthropic SDK (sync, wrapped in asyncio.to_thread),
SQLAlchemy 2 + asyncpg, Alembic (pure op.execute SQL, IF NOT EXISTS pattern),
Postgres 16 + pgvector, structlog, pytest (async tests via pytest-asyncio)

