## Implemented bot commands

/ping              — health check, no defer needed
/start             — DM-based onboarding (7 questions), persists Player + PlayerProfile
/begin             — generates case via CaseGenerator (LLM), seeds Facts + FactLayers,
                     deferred, broad except Exception logs full traceback
/case              — shows active case embed + last 5 notes
/akte              — numbered list of Facts showing current perceived layer + Reality Score
/spur <nr>         — shows perceived layer for fact #nr, drops reality_score -0.02,
                     triggers corruption if below DRIFT_THRESHOLD (0.7), runs TimelineScorer
/befragen <name>   — NPC witness query, creates claimed FactLayer, drops reality_score -0.01,
                     runs TimelineScorer
/note <text> [spur=<nr>]  — saves PlayerNote, optionally pins snapshot of perceived layer
                            for later comparison, runs TimelineScorer
/journal           — lists all notes with timestamp + ⚠️ marker if snapshot drifted
/vergleichen <nr>  — three-panel diff: note text | snapshot | current perceived layer,
                     word-level diff via difflib.ndiff in a ```diff block
/admin_seed_timeline <case_uuid>  — [admin] seeds investigator/shadow_a/shadow_b timelines
/admin_force_phase <phase>        — [admin] sets case phase directly via apply_transition

