## Phase transition thresholds (case_lifecycle.py)

opening      → investigation : action_count >= 3
investigation → first_reveal  : action_count >= 10 AND unique_npcs >= 2
first_reveal → second_reveal  : action_count >= 20 AND reality_score <= 0.60
second_reveal → finale        : action_count >= 30 AND reality_score <= 0.30

action_count = note_count + befragen_count + spur_count
  note_count     = COUNT(PlayerNote WHERE case_id)
  befragen_count = COUNT(FactLayer WHERE layer_type="claimed" for case's facts)
  spur_count     = COUNT(FactLayer WHERE layer_type="perceived" AND version > 1)
unique_npcs    = COUNT(DISTINCT FactLayer.modified_by WHERE layer_type="claimed")

Lifecycle is checked at end of /note, /spur, /befragen via _check_lifecycle(session, case, player).
On transition: apply_transition writes case_phase_history row + plain-text followup message to player.

